{
  "stem": "18778.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as soon as she heard that we were coming to England, or my mother got in touch with her via the telegraph communication system on board, and she requested us to come to York.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So-- and she was friendly with the Rowntree family, Rowntree chocolates, which is equal to Hershey chocolates.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were guests of the Rowntree family in York for several months.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had to embark on a small German merchant ship, the R-A-K-O-T-I-S.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There-- this was not a luxury ship.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And most of the people, about 250 people, were in mass quarters.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Only the committee people had cabins.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had a steady stream of visitors using our bath and our shower, and shaving in our bathroom and so on, and so all the other committee people as well.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father and I were taking a walk on deck, and I noticed rolled up rolls lying along the deck against the wall.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It looked like rolled up carpets.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said to my dad, are they going to put new carpets on this ship?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He says, those are cannon.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You see, Hitler was ready.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Hitler was ready.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We crossed the channel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know how long it took, but we arrived in Southampton from there by train to London.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From this train station in London, per horse and buggy to the hotel-- England was a quaint-- quaint country when we got there in 1939.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I guess after a day or two at the hotel, we took the train to York.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we lived on the Rowntree Estate for three months.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the meantime, the people who came to England were guests.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were very special.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Arrangements had been made for them.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
